    INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [p.ProductCategory2] ON [p2].[CategoryId] = [p.ProductCategory2].[Id]
    WHERE [p2].[Status] = 1
    ORDER BY [p2].[DateCreated] DESC, [p2].[Id]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t2] ON [p.ProductTags].[ProductId] = [t2].[Id]
ORDER BY [t2].[DateCreated] DESC, [t2].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

VALUES (@p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, 0),

""SET NOCOUNT ON;
DELETE FROM [ProductImages]
WHERE [Id] = @p0;
SELECT @@ROWCOUNT;

DECLARE @inserted1 TABLE ([Id] int, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [ProductImages] USING (
VALUES (@p1, @p2, @p3, 0),
(@p4, @p5, @p6, 1),
(@p7, @p8, @p9, 2)) AS i ([Caption], [Image], [ProductId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([Caption], [Image], [ProductId])
VALUES (i.[Caption], i.[Image], i.[ProductId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted1;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [ProductImages] t
